<!-- Why Over Time Section -->
<div style="background-color:#ffffff; padding:70px 20px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">

    <h2 style="font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;color:#1d4939;font-size:2rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:20px;">
      Why This Work Happens Over Time
    </h2>

    <p style="font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;color:#444;margin-bottom:16px;">
      Fertility isn’t a single moment — it’s a process. Egg and sperm development, hormone signaling, and nutrient status are shaped over months, not days.
    </p>

    <p style="font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;color:#444;margin-bottom:18px;">
      A three-month window allows nutrition and lifestyle support to align with how the body naturally works.
    </p>

    <ul style="font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;color:#444;line-height:1.7;">
      <li>Clarify priorities instead of reacting</li>
      <li>Build consistency</li>
      <li>Adjust support as your cycle or treatment plan evolves</li>
    </ul>

    <p style="font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;color:#444;margin-top:20px;">
      Together, we focus on what matters now — the areas that can have the greatest impact on your fertility journey — and support steady progress toward what matters most to you: building your family.
    </p>

  </div>
</div>


<!-- Who It's For Section -->
<div style="background-color:#f1f5f3; padding:70px 20px;">
