    <ul style="font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;color:#444;line-height:1.8;">
      <li>Trying to conceive and unsure where to focus</li>
      <li>Preparing for an upcoming IVF or treatment cycle</li>
      <li>Between cycles and wanting to support egg or sperm health</li>
      <li>Navigating PCOS, endometriosis, irregular cycles, or insulin resistance</li>
      <li>Experiencing unexplained infertility</li>
      <li>Coming off birth control and wanting to support cycle health</li>
      <li>Wanting guidance without restrictive dieting or fear-based messaging</li>
    </ul>

  </div>
